Interface Model

All Superinterfaces:
ModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface Model
extends ModelObject

A representation of the model object 'Model'.

The following features are supported:

  • Physical Models
  • Business Models
  • Property Types
  • Property Categories
